Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:26.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:82270,86608}If you're this determined, I can postpone\Nthe shutdown of the Wellington Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:28.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:87525,88318}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.86,0:01:32.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:88860,92697}I will also cover the salaries of the miners\Nand the costs of further research.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:36.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93197,96492}Since I am so kind\Nto give you this much,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:40.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96492,100079}you will have to take\Nresponsibility for everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:44.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100079,104709}To prove that you are taking it seriously,\Nyou will let me have your most precious thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:48.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104709,108463}That means you will have\Nto leave Lassie with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:52.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108838,112508}If it turns out that you were right\Nand there is still hope for the mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:54.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112508,114135}I will give Lassie back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:58.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114135,118097}But if it does not,\NLassie will become mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:00.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119265,120266}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:05.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120266,125021}Do you trust\Nyour father this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125021,126064}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:07.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126939,127815}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:09.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127815,129609}We will find more coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:12.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129609,132862}Then I will take Lassie back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:17.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136032,137367}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:31.21,lassie episode,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:145917,151214}{\blur0.5\fad(300,0)\pos(320,300)}Do Your Best, John!\NProtect Lassie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:36.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155218,156678}Good morning, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:40.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157136,160181}Ah, good morning, John.\NI ate before you got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160181,162433}Dad hasn't returned\Nsince yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:44.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163559,164894}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:47.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164894,167980}I returned after you\Nwent to sleep last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167980,170817}But you're a big boy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:52.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170817,172527}You also have Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172527,174529}Let's see, what's next…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:55.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174529,175446}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175905,177323}I have to go to work already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:02:59.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178533,179617}I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:03.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182495,183705}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184455,185623}…is no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:11.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187250,191379}But now's not the time\Nfor moping around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:12.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191713,192714}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192714,195550}When the school ends,\NI'll go to the mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195550,196467}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201848,204142}Who was I talking to exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:27.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205351,207603}I have to do something, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:43.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222618,223911}Sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223911,225455}I knew I'd find you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:49.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225455,229000}Oh, no. How long\Nhave I been asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229000,230668}It's ten o'clock already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:53.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230668,233629}This place is pretty quiet at ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233629,235965}You should go home\Nand get proper rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236382,237633}Ah, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:00.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237633,240261}There's a lot of work I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:05.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240261,245600}That's enough, Sam. I've received\Nanother notice from the Duke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:06.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245600,246559}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246559,249771}He wrote he would postpone\Nthe closure of the mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:14.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249771,254108}We got funds to continue with the\Ngeological survey, just like you asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254108,255359}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:18.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255735,258571}The Duke will pay for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:21.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258571,261824}We'll be able to pay salaries\Nto everyone, as usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:24.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261824,264285}But when I spoke\Nto him recently, he—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:27.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264285,267663}Don't sweat the small stuff, Sam!\NBe happy with what you're given!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:30.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267663,270082}I'm sure your pressure\Ngot him thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:30.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270082,270875}Mhm…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:37.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274170,277882}But what caused this\Ncomplete change of mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277882,280927}Don't bother about it now!\NWe're here to say thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:43.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281552,283429}Please wait inside for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283429,284347}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:51.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289268,291896}Be quiet! How long are you\Ngonna keep barking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:52.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291896,292647}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:55.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293064,295107}What's she doing in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:58.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295817,298361}Aren't you ashamed of yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:04:59.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298361,299487}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299904,301447}About Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301447,303574}I don't know\Nwhat you told to my son,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:06.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303574,306702}but to take a beloved dog\Nfrom a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306702,308412}That's just vicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:13.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310706,313334}Sam, calm down! Sam…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:16.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313334,316587}No matter how\Nmarvelous that dog is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:21.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316587,321175}I'm not senile enough to trade a mere dog\Nfor the mine's administration rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:25.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321175,325263}It was a manly agreement\Nbetween John and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325263,327098}What do you mean,\Nmanly agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327098,329559}He's only 11 years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329559,331102}What of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:35.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331102,335481}Shouldn't you respect\Nyour son's spirit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:39.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335481,339360}Or are you telling me that\Nyou don't believe in yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:42.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340570,342154}What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:45.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342154,345032}John trusts you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:48.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345032,348369}He still believes that\Nyou will find more coal,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:50.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348369,350997}perhaps even more than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:58.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353833,358546}You should respond to\Nyour son's trust, Mr. Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:05.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360965,365303}Therefore, for the calculation here,\Nwe multiply 4 times 2 and get 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:09.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365303,369307}Then 4 times 5, we get 20.\N4 times 1, we get 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:14.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369307,374770}After we carry the remainder and sum\Nall the digits, we get the first product, 608.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:17.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375062,377064}Something's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377064,378774}John's acting weird today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379817,380943}John…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:29.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386991,389702}That's all for today's lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:30.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389702,390828}John Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392163,393581}John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:35.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394749,395333}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:40.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395750,400171}Ask your classmates what today's lesson\Nwas about and make sure you don't fall behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400171,402924}Yes? What the lesson was about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:46.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404133,406093}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:49.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406093,409847}You weren't paying attention\Nin today's class at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409847,411849}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411849,413976}Don't be so down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:57.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413976,417855}You'll see Lassie in a moment.\NShe'll cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422693,424028}Lassie's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:08.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427865,428783}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429867,431035}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432328,433537}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:17.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436540,437291}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:18.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437959,438709}How did you…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:27.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444090,447301}Why did you come back, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:30.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447301,450388}Let's go to the Duke's place later\Nand ask him what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:39.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457812,459981}Here you are, as I had expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:44.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460648,464235}You are one hell of a dog\Nto have escaped from that cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466195,468531}So Lassie escaped\Nfrom the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:50.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469281,470741}Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:53.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470741,473411}Didn't you train her to escape\Nto begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:54.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473411,474412}Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:59.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474412,479417}Have your dog escape back to you,\Nthen sell it high to another fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479417,480876}Pretty smart, I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:03.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480876,483087}But you can't deceive\Ngood old Heinz.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483087,485840}You got it all wrong!\NAs if I could do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:07.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485840,487383}Whatever.\NYou're going with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487383,488759}Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489552,491762}Lassie… I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:15.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491762,495599}But I must keep\Nmy promise to the Duke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495599,497351}I will come back for you, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:19.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498894,499562}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499562,501105}Time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509447,510239}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510239,511907}What happened to Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:35.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511907,515578}Nothing at all.\NShe'll come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:38.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515578,518205}I just let her stay with\NPriscilla's grandfather for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:41.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518664,521042}What do you mean,\Nyou let her stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:44.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521500,524754}Priscilla's grandfather\Nloves dogs a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525087,527715}And that makes it right\Nto let him have Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:50.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527715,530384}It'll be fine.\NI'll recover her soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:51.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531010,531761}What are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532636,534638}To the mine.\NI'm going to help Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:58.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535681,538309}But the mine is shut down…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540311,541771}It's moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548402,550529}{\i1}Let me help you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:13.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550529,553574}{\i1}There must be something I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593906,595574}Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:56.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595574,596700}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596700,599745}Oh, no, children can't enter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:02.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599745,602790}I want to help you\Nfind the new deposits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:03.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602790,603833}What did you…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603833,605626}No, you should go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:06.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605626,606794}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607336,609713}Please let him come down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:11.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609713,611173}I'll talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:13.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612675,613843}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:20.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619974,620975}Dad, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622101,624478}You want to help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:26.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624770,626730}I want to do something, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:29.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629233,629984}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:34.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630860,634697}We are digging a new shaft,\Nin a new location.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:37.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634697,637700}We're going to take rock samples\Nfrom different layers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:42.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638450,642204}It's hard to dig through this soil,\Nbut there is one thing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:46.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643205,646417}I'd like you to use this\Nto collect rock samples.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:47.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646834,647877}Dad, does it mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:51.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647877,651589}Yes. Let's do our best\Nand find a new deposit, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:52.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651922,652923}Yes. Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:56.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654675,656427}For Lassie's sake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657178,658804}Dad, you knew about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660222,661432}Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:05.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662975,665519}Yes. I'll do what I can.
Comment: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:16.23,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:676238,676238}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:35.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692588,695716}Mr. Carraclough, is it reasonable\Nto let your son do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:40.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697509,700221}Maybe not quite, but this time,\NI want to let him be part of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:42.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701347,702932}Just don't let him fall down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:02.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720491,722493}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726205,728874}My house is full of dirty men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:21.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740678,741470}John…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:30.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749395,750437}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:33.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751230,753107}She didn't come today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:39.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758237,759613}John…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763701,764702}It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:47.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764702,767454}If you flee, I'll get fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:49.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767454,769248}So I used my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:53.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769248,773168}Not even you can dig\Nthrough an iron plate, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790102,791687}Be careful, it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:12.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791979,792855}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800321,802740}I happened to hear\Na peculiar thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:27.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802740,807161}The Duke got tired of sitting still and decided\Nto return to Scotland all of the sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:28.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807161,808245}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:30.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809038,810247}What about Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811206,812958}What if he takes her along?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:35.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812958,815169}Don't waste your time\Non useless rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:37.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815169,817629}Just focus on mining\Nand getting us more coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:40.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817629,820049}We've gotta satisfy\Nthe damn geezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:43.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820049,823969}You're right. Failing after all this\Nwould be unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:47.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823969,827931}By the way, I heard you and your lady\Nhave gotten yourselves a baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:51.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827931,831727}That's all the more reason\Nwhy we've got to find more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:55.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831727,835022}What kind of a father will I be\Nif I can't even afford milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:56.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835022,836523}It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:57.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836523,837691}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:59.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837691,839276}It all boils down\Nto responsibility, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:10.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850079,850996}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:13.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851538,853791}Are you going to the mine again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:17.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853791,857252}I'm sorry. I know I haven't\Nplayed with you lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:18.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857252,858045}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858045,860798}John! Lassie is going to Scotland!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:21.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860798,861590}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:25.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861590,865010}My Dad heard this from\Nthe mansion's servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:27.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865010,867971}The Duke is going back\Ntoday by the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:31.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867971,871475}They canceled the order for the dog food,\Nstarting from tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871475,872684}He's taking Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:37.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872684,877106}Tell me, can't we get Lassie back\Nbefore they leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879191,880484}We can't yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:41.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880484,881360}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881360,882528}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:47.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883237,887366}When we find new deposits, it will all\Ngo back to normal and we'll get Lassie back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887366,889076}Sorry. I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:51.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889076,891703}There are a lot of things\Nthat I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:52.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891703,892538}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:15:02.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896375,902089}So these are the samples we want to send\Nto the university laboratory for analysis?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902089,904925}Yes. We're going to study\Nthe age of each layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:10.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905426,910097}The layer we'd been digging the coal from\Nwas very old, from the Paleozoic era.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:13.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910097,913725}If we get to know the age\Nof the soil in different layers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913725,915936}it should be easier\Nto find more coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:20.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917479,920941}It appears you are far more\Ncompetent than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:22.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921775,922443}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:25.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922860,925070}All right, I'm going to mail it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:27.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925487,927072}Okay! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:37.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936290,937666}That selfish John.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:55.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951597,955851}You've got a two-day train trip ahead of you.\NTime to say goodbye to Yorkshire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:22.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981168,982544}Oh? Heinz.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982961,984296}It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:25.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984296,985672}Have you brought\Nyet another dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986131,987382}Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:30.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987382,990844}I brought it all the way\Nfrom Yorkshire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990844,992554}Grandfather really likes dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:34.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992554,994556}Will he ever stop buying new ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:39.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994556,999645}Ah, but I believe you know\Nthis one very well, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:42.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001897,1002773}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:48.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004525,1008362}That boy called John…\NHe is quite an extraordinary child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:54.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008362,1014868}He didn't come crying to me to let him see\NLassie after he had left her under my care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014868,1016078}Priscilla…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:58.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016078,1018580}I strongly acknowledge\Nthe will of that boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:01.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018580,1021124}and for this reason I agreed\Nto keep her as a deposit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021375,1023210}As a deposit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024127,1025337}Priscilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:09.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025337,1029758}If you told me now\Nto return Lassie to John,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:15.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029758,1035806}don't you think it would be demeaning to\Nhis decision, thus disrespectful to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038100,1039017}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:23.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039977,1043564}Here, Dad said I should get it to you\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045065,1046692}Please read it quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046692,1049152}What is the rush? Let me see…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:31.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049152,1051822}We got the lab results already?\NSo what do they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:33.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052239,1053865}I told you not to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060872,1062416}What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062416,1063458}They're too recent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:44.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063458,1064084}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:45.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064376,1065127}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:48.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065127,1068547}All the samples are from layers\Nthat are too young to yield coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:53.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069464,1073218}However,\Nthe possibility is not zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073218,1075971}It's like saying it is zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:56.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075971,1076888}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076888,1078765}So if there are no deposits left—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:17:59.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078765,1079600}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:04.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079600,1084563}Does it mean that Lassie…\Nwill never go back to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084563,1086607}Stay calm, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:08.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086607,1088692}How can I be calm!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088692,1090152}John! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090902,1093947}He's not the only one\Nwho's shocked with this information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:16.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095699,1096908}Manager…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121058,1122351}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148919,1150295}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155133,1156385}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:23.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162557,1163975}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:27.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163975,1167688}Colin and Sandy told me\NI'd find you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:29.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167688,1169272}They were sure you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:34.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170148,1174361}It is your special place, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:37.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175028,1177155}John and Colin, and Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:39.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177155,1179199}And recently also Priscilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:45.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182244,1185455}Don't forget Lassie, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185455,1187040}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:49.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187040,1189292}That's right. Lassie, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198093,1199678}Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:03.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200929,1203306}Everyone is waiting\Nfor you outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203849,1205183}Who is waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207436,1208061}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209104,1211064}Sandy… Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211523,1212774}John, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:15.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212774,1215569}You have us, so you don't have\Nto do everything by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:21.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219072,1221032}Let's go home, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:24.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221032,1224035}Mom is also waiting for us, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224035,1225120}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:33.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231001,1233545}Why did you put iron sheets\Nonly in Lassie's cage?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:38.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234713,1238759}Well, in fact I put these\Nso that she won't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:39.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238759,1239676}She escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:46.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239676,1246224}Oh, well, I got her locked up well,\Nbut she did try to escape back to Yorkshire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:48.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246224,1248935}She must've been\Ntrained to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:53.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248935,1253315}Make her owner a load of cash,\Nescape, then get sold to another collector.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:56.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254107,1256234}But I, Heinz, saw through this—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:58.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256234,1258361}John would not do\Nanything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:03.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258695,1263867}So Lassie didn't know when John\Nwould be back, and couldn't sit still…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264201,1266828}She couldn't be patient,\Ncouldn't bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:12.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267162,1272209}I'm sure the same goes for John. He wants\Nto see Lassie and can hardly bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273001,1275504}Grandfather doesn't\Nunderstand anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276713,1278340}Miss, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:19.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278340,1279549}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:24.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281676,1284888}You want to go to John's place, right?\NHere, you're free!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:29.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288433,1289935}I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:37.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296733,1297943}Don't open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:39.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297943,1299444}Don't open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299444,1301112}No! Open it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:49.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307702,1309037}What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:51.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309037,1311039}Go, Lassie! Go to John!
Comment: 0,0:21:57.37,0:21:57.37,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1317379,1317379}Preview
