Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:09.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1325011,1329099}{\i1}Without food,\Nchased by unruly dogs, tired…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329099,1331560}{\i1}Now she faces a gun.
